sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Admin
    participant FE as Admin Portal<br/>Next.js :3001
    participant BE as Backend<br/>Express API
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL
    participant Discord as Discord<br/>Bot Service
    participant N8N as N8N<br/>Incident Handler

    Admin ->> FE: Buka /admin/tickets<br/>Klik Input Tiket Incident
    activate FE
    FE -->> Admin: Tampil Form Input Tiket Incident
    deactivate FE

    Admin ->> FE: Isi form - Judul, Deskripsi,<br/>Prioritas, Severity, Suspect Area, Pelapor
    activate FE
    FE ->> FE: Validasi semua field required
    Admin ->> FE: Klik Submit Incident
    FE ->> BE: POST /api/tickets/create (type=INCIDENT)
    deactivate FE
    activate BE

    BE ->> BE: Ticket Service - createTicket (INCIDENT)
    BE ->> BE: Classifier - deteksi severity dan area
    Note over BE: Hasil: category, priority,<br/>suspect_area, keywords

    BE ->> DB: ticket.create (type=INCIDENT, status=OPEN)
    activate DB
    DB -->> BE: ticket id dan ticketNumber
    deactivate DB

    BE ->> DB: activity.create (TICKET_CREATED)
    BE ->> DB: activity.create (incident_detected)

    par Notifikasi Incident
        BE ->> Discord: postIncidentEmbed (ticket, priority=HIGH)
        activate Discord
        Discord ->> Discord: Buat thread label INCIDENT
        Discord -->> BE: threadId, messageId
        deactivate Discord
    and
        BE ->> N8N: triggerWorkflow (incident.created)
        activate N8N
        N8N ->> N8N: Workflow 3 - Incident Handler
        Note over N8N: AI analisis root cause<br/>dan langkah mitigasi
        N8N -->> BE: classification result
        deactivate N8N
    end

    BE -->> FE: 201 Created - ticketId, type=INCIDENT
    deactivate BE
    FE -->> Admin: Redirect ke detail incident